Content: [telegram] <Regnar> I'm messing around with it right now, idk the team that made it though so definitely do your research on them before depositing funds. I put a few in to see how it works. It so far seems really nice tbh. You go to the site, create a wallet and they download the backup key to your computer (wherever you want, could do USB too) and then when you want to login, it either remembers where you keep it and you use a password, or if you use incognito browsers, you just click import from backup, and browse to the location you stored the backup, then use password.
